               <msContents>
                  <summary>List of the Mǝlṭan Hymns for each feast; Image of Peter and Paul; Introduction to the Four Gospels; List of the sections for Matthew and Introduction for Matthew; Gospel of Matthew; List of the sections for Mark and Introduction for Mark; Gospel of Mark; List of the sections for Luke and Introduction for Luke; Gospel of Luke; List of sections for John and Introduction for John; Gospel of John; Revelation of John, 1:1-4:1</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
